.TH "LIGHTNING-WALLET-NOTES-TAG-COUNT" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-wallet-notes-tag-count \- FEAT-2033 verb
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning wallet-notes-tag-count
.SH DESCRIPTION
verb for lightning CLI (FEAT-2033).
.PP
Queries the per-wallet SQLite store and returns note counts grouped by tag.
Returns an error gracefully if no wallet database is found.
.PP
Output: JSON from CLN.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning(1)
